    <userTask id="ut_template_lumprianm_redyellowFlagsChecklist" name="[TIETO] Red/Yellow Flags Checklist" flowable:candidateGroups="clinicians" flowable:formKey="form_lumbalgia_redFlags" flowable:formFieldValidation="false">
      <documentation>Template: Lumbalgia Checklist (Red Flags section). The clinician answers the ICS Red Flags questionnaire (age, neoplastic history, weight loss, fever, corticosteroids, IV drug use, trauma, recent spinal surgery, neurological deficit, saddle anaesthesia, urinary/faecal retention, night pain). Result: variable redFlagsPresent (boolean). PENDING ADJUSTMENT of the exact question list with the client.</documentation>
      <extensionElements>
        <flowable:task-candidates-type><![CDATA[all]]></flowable:task-candidates-type>
        <flowable:allowed-input-item><![CDATA[ehrId]]></flowable:allowed-input-item>
        <flowable:allowed-input-item><![CDATA[templateId]]></flowable:allowed-input-item>
        <flowable:allowed-input-item><![CDATA[archetypes]]></flowable:allowed-input-item>
        <flowable:allowed-output-item><![CDATA[redFlags_object_version_id]]></flowable:allowed-output-item>
        <design:stencilid><![CDATA[FormTask]]></design:stencilid>
        <design:stencilsuperid><![CDATA[Task]]></design:stencilsuperid>
      </extensionElements>
    </userTask>
